  "title": "Roasted Garlic And Potato Soup",
  "subtitle": "A blended soup, smooth and warm.",
  "excerpt": "Roasted Garlic And Potato Soup. A smooth blended soup with simple components, vegetables sweated low, stock added, blitzed at the end.",
